abstract: Stocks fall sharply after Federal Reserve issues report about United States economy, and also suffer from benchmark crude oil price sinking to lowest level in almost six years.
lead_paragraph: The Fed strengthened its assessment of the American economy, a signal to investors that it is moving closer to raising rates.
snippet: The Fed strengthened its assessment of the American economy, a signal to investors that it is moving closer to raising rates.

headline.main: Sell-Off After Fed Signals Eventual Rate Increase
